                    <p class="utterance">Hier in . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hier in Paris.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hier in Paris.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Ja.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
