                    <p class="utterance">Yes. And on . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">On the 11th of April . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">The 11th of April . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">. . . in the year &#39;41, I . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Received this paper.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">. . . received this paper.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Was it mailed to you or transmitted by hand [?]?</p>
