                    <p class="utterance">Sent by mail. [unintelligible]</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Notified[?] you by mail . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">. . . that he had gone voluntarily to work in Germany.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
