                    <p class="utterance">And I remained with the child.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">And when were you arrested?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Bertha Goldwasser</b>
                    <p class="utterance">On the 16th of July in the year &#39;42.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">That was approximately a year later.</p>
